yn: <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Witch_of_Portobello">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Witc...</a><br />i am always annoyed when things that sound interesting are written in a boring manner <br />he epitomizes that for me<br /><br />me: does tao lin write in a boring manner?<br /><br />...<br /><br />me: my infectious smile <br />"sleep is a skilled magician, it changes the proportions of things, the distances between them, it separates people and they're lying next to each other, brings them together and they can barely see one another, the woman is sleeping only a few yards away from him and he cannot reach her, yet it's so easy to go from port to starboard."<br /> <br />Carolyn: wow<br /><br />me: like dat?<br /> <br />Carolyn: yea<br /> <br />me: made me think of us a bit<br /> <br />Carolyn: yea :)<br />i like the nautical terms in dere too</span>
